@MLN111_HostAddress = http://localhost:5196
@token = 

### Health
GET {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/health/database

### Register (user thuong)
POST {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@demo.local",
  "displayName": "Sinh vien Demo",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}

### Login admin (seed khi app chay lan dau)
POST {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mln111.local",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### Me
GET {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tao phong quiz (Admin)
POST {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Giai cap va dan toc - Demo",
  "description": "Chuong 3 MLN",
  "secondsPerQuestion": 20
}

### State phong (poll dong bo)
GET {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/rooms/{roomId}/state

### Leaderboard
GET {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/rooms/{roomId}/leaderboard

### AI - trang thai (co ApiKey chua)
GET {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/ai/status

### AI - GPT-5-nano (JWT + OpenAI ApiKey trong Ai:ApiKey hoac OPENAI_API_KEY)
POST {{MLN111_HostAddress}}/api/ai/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Giai thich ngan ve dau tranh giai cap theo quan diem Mac?"
}
